content_description: A group of friends energetically dancing and posing in front of a brightly lit Eiffel Tower replica at night.

High.reason: Intense group movement including a kick and dynamic camera motion as the lights change color.

Medium.reason: Initial posing and coordinated dance moves with moderate energy and steady camera work.

Low.reason: The group relaxes and laughs after the main action, showing a more candid and less intense moment.
